ZH: 我们明天要去郊外野餐。
EN: We are going for a picnic in the countryside tomorrow.

ZH: 我们带了很多美食去野餐。
EN: We brought a lot of delicious food for the picnic.

ZH: 野餐时可以呼吸新鲜空气。
EN: Picnics allow us to breathe fresh air.

ZH: 我喜欢在公园野餐，可以享受大自然的美景。
EN: I love having picnics in the park, enjoying the beauty of nature.

ZH: 我准备了野餐垫子和毯子。
EN: I prepared picnic mats and blankets.

ZH: 野餐时可以和家人一起共度美好时光。
EN: Picnics are a great way to spend quality time with family.

ZH: 在湖边野餐是一个很浪漫的选择。
EN: Having a picnic by the lake is a romantic choice.

ZH: 小朋友们喜欢在草地上野餐。
EN: Children enjoy picnicking on the grass.

ZH: 请大家提前准备好野餐食物。
EN: Please prepare picnic food in advance.

ZH: 野餐篮子里装满了水果和点心。
EN: The picnic basket is filled with fruits and snacks.

ZH: 野餐是一个放松身心的好方式。
EN: Picnicking is a great way to relax and unwind.

ZH: 我将带上音乐让野餐更加愉快。
EN: I will bring music to make the picnic more enjoyable.

ZH: 晴朗的天气最适合野餐。
EN: Sunny weather is ideal for a picnic.

ZH: 我们可以在公园的草地上搭起帐篷进行野餐。
EN: We can set up a tent on the grass in the park for a picnic.

