EN: I bought a new picnic blanket that is lightweight and easy to carry.

ZH: 在乡村野餐是一种很好的放松方式。
EN: Picnicking in the countryside is a great way to relax.

ZH: 她带着孩子们去郊游野餐。
EN: She took the children for an outing and picnic.
